---
title: Hearty Steak and Potato Hash with Smoky Ketchup
description: A tasty one-pan wonder! Steak, shredded Brussels, roasted potatoes and squash gets a toss in the pan for a quick crunchy exterior. And of course, it wouldn't be complete without a drizzle of smoky ketchup!
